476
00:33:26,087 --> 00:33:27,422
Bersama-sama, sebenarnya.

477
00:33:32,135 --> 00:33:33,469
Sudah tentu,

478
00:33:33,970 --> 00:33:35,596
Tae-yeong ialah

479
00:33:36,472 --> 00:33:37,807
bersama kita selamanya.

480
00:33:49,027 --> 00:33:50,987
Saya… saya minta maaf.

481
00:33:52,405 --> 00:33:54,115
Anda boleh hubungi kami.

482
00:33:55,616 --> 00:33:57,452
Kami di sini untuk anda sentiasa.

483
00:33:58,619 --> 00:34:00,079
Kami duo Marin.

484
00:34:00,663 --> 00:34:02,206
Kami sedia berkhidmat untuk anda.

485
00:34:03,833 --> 00:34:06,169
- Sayang Tae-yeong.
- Saya akan.

486
00:34:06,252 --> 00:34:07,754
Ack.

487
00:34:12,592 --> 00:34:14,218
Tae-yeong.

488
00:34:19,891 --> 00:34:21,142
Huggies.

489
00:34:32,653 --> 00:34:33,946
Mereka berpacaran!

490
00:35:11,526 --> 00:35:12,652
Ya, siapa itu?

491
00:35:12,735 --> 00:35:14,529
& Lt; i & gt; Selamat petang. Kami berkawan dengan Gun-woo.</i>

492
00:35:14,612 --> 00:35:18,616
saya nampak. Nah, Gun-woo tiada di rumah
dan dia mungkin balik lambat.

493
00:35:18,699 --> 00:35:22,453
Oh, kita sepatutnya berjumpa.
Saya mungkin datang awal.

494
00:35:23,037 --> 00:35:25,331
Tidak mengapa jika kita menunggu di dalam?

495
00:35:26,791 --> 00:35:28,918
<i>Kami berkawan kerana</i>
<i>kita pergi ke gim yang sama.</i>

496
00:35:29,001 --> 00:35:29,961
saya nampak.

497
